# Files/directories excluded from the shinyapps.io deploy bundle.
#
# IMPORTANT: rsconnect matches lines with EXACT string comparison against the
# immediate contents of each directory. No globs, no trailing slashes, no
# nested paths. To exclude files inside a subdirectory, put another
# .rscignore there (see data/.rscignore).

